孺若花柳。姦人妻，惑人夫，刁風月，弄牆隙，交合行淫，行淫交合，迷姦強暴者，不絕於國也。堂姊表妹、兄嫂內娣、朋女友孫、皆可慾淫。愚女信徒，秘書病人，及其鄉里鄰舍，長幼無一倖免。娼盜口穴逢迎，奪僕童貞操。浪師股乳招搖，誘學子心性。或交合時陰錄春宮，分別時皇皇然脅之，又得幾回歡愉。女甫口角，輒奔舊愛，哭啼哭啼，又變嘿咻嘿咻。男欲內發，女言不可，騷首之間，閉穴全受。縱情荒淫，誠此地之謂也。"},{"pid":"64325d853f3d762fc1f6a351fec1870e5a2b352c","tid":2339760,"uid":71913,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b1ad3ec040b1b9c3130d89d82670f8ec2b0e49be","tid":2339760,"uid":304281,"like":44,"dislike":4,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"9a6819792f356fc8ebf3bd4e432b5ae15440e653","tid":2339760,"uid":72009,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"9a99766a3b4fbd23fc5298a8b4213de496aa9f69","tid":2339760,"uid":143727,"like":11,"dislike":200,"score":-189,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"公道啲講句，台灣政府搞唔起經濟，先會出現依啲食洋腸女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果佢地市民人工高都唔會個個想去發達國家生活"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"no，台妹追求性滿足，老實，洋搶勁Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"台妹真係放蕩啲<br />\n睇SWAG就知<br />\n賣片不突止，網友仲可以俾錢扑嘢<br />\n香港、日本女仔始終都有啲道德枷鎖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"笑撚左"},{"pid":"d9d57e13b3362421bfd2ca886154ccf70ca18c7c","tid":2339760,"uid":346660,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"個女仔係機師？真係睇唔出"},{"pid":"0c41f906c57328572a66b0d35e5272dfed07bd11","tid":2339760,"uid":337052,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">被瞎指為「案771」爆乳辣照瘋傳 大馬網紅：感謝台灣網友關注</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3391038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3391038&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=3c92d47a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3391038&h=206a85d2\" data-auto-link 